{{Distinguish|Template:User talk page}}
== Usage ==
This template may be placed on pages in [[WP:OWNTALK|user talk pages]] in order to differentiate them from pages containing [[WP:NS|encyclopedic content]]. It is recommended that it be included via <code><nowiki>{{subst:usertalkpage}}</nowiki></code> so that it will be displayed even on mirror sites that don't use this template.

=== Parameters ===
* {{tnull|usertalkpage|2=logo=yes|3=noindex=yes}}
** {{para|logo|<var>yes</var>}}&nbsp;– shows the Wikipedia logo on the left (default {{var|hidden}})
** {{para|logo|<var>right</var>}}&nbsp;- shows the Wikipedia logo on the right (default {{var|hidden}})
** {{para|noindex|<var>yes</var>}}&nbsp;– prevents external search engines from indexing the page (default {{var|no}})
** {{para|rounded|<var>yes</var>}}&nbsp;- makes the container's border rounded (default {{var|no}})
** {{para|border-radius|<var>15px</var>}}&nbsp;- changes the border radius, if <code>rounded={{var|yes}}</code> is also set (default {{var|15px}})
** {{para|border-s|<var>1</var>}}&nbsp;- the size of the border (default {{var|1}})
** {{para|border-c|<var>#ffc9c9</var>}}&nbsp;- the color of the border (default {{var|#ffc9c9}})
** {{para|background|<var>#fffff3</var>}}&nbsp;- changes the background color (default {{var|#fffff3}})

